            Ready to embark on a journey of creative exploration? Your vision is
            our expertise - together, let's create <b>Pure Vibes</b> . Whether you're
            seeking to boost your digital presence, redefine your brand or plan a
            memorable event – we've got you covered. Let's craft your brand's story
            together. Contact us today and discover the power of
            <b>Pure Vibes</b> – where creativity knows no bounds!
          </p>
          <p>
            <a href='/contact' class='footer-link-more'>Book Us</a>
          </p>
          <p>
            <i class='bi bi-telephone'></i> (+254)743870297
          </p>
          <p>
            <i class='bi bi-envelope'></i> info@purevibes.co.ke
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class='col-6 col-lg-2'>
          <h3 class='footer-heading'>Navigation</h3>
          <ul class='footer-links list-unstyled'>
            <li>
              <a href='/'><i class='bi bi-chevron-right'></i>Home</a>
            </li>
            <li>
              <a href='/services'
                ><i class='bi bi-chevron-right'></i>Work with Us</a
              >
            </li>
            <li>
              <a href='contact.html'
                ><i class='bi bi-chevron-right'></i>Podcast</a
              >
            </li>
            <li>
              <a href='/about'><i class='bi bi-chevron-right'></i>About</a>
            </li>
            <li>
              <a href='/contact'
                ><i class='bi bi-chevron-right'></i>Contact Us</a
              >
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class='col-6 col-lg-2'>
          <h3 class='footer-heading'>Categories</h3>
          <ul class='footer-links list-unstyled'>
            <li>
              <a href='/category/business'
                ><i class='bi bi-chevron-right'></i>Business</a
              >
            </li>
            <li>
              <a href='/category/lifestyle'
                ><i class='bi bi-chevron-right'></i>Lifestyle & Health</a
              >
            </li>
            <li>
              <a href='/category/fashion'
                ><i class='bi bi-chevron-right'></i>Fashion</a
              >
            </li>
            <li>
              <a href='/category/travel'
                ><i class='bi bi-chevron-right'></i>Travel & Food</a
              >
            </li>
            <li>
              <a href='/category/tech'
                ><i class='bi bi-chevron-right'></i>Tech</a
              >
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class='col-lg-4'>
          <h3 class='footer-heading'>Recent Posts</h3>

          <ul class='footer-links footer-blog-entry list-unstyled'>
            {
              posts.slice(0, 4).map((post) => (
                <li>
                  <a
                    href={`/blog/${post.slug}`}
                    class='d-flex align-items-center'
                  >
                    <img
                      src={post.data.heroImage}
                      width=''
                      height=''
                      alt={post.data.title}
                      class='img-fluid me-3'
                    />
                    <div>
                      <div class='post-meta d-block'>
                        <span class='date'>{post.data.category}</span>
                        <span class='mx-1'>&bullet;</span>
                        <span>
                          <FormattedDate date={post.data.pubDate} />
                        </span>
                      </div>
                      <span>{post.data.title}</span>
                    </div>
                  </a>
                </li>
              ))
            }
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class='footer-legal'>
    <div class='container'>
      <div class='row justify-content-between'>
        <div class='col-md-6 text-center text-md-start mb-3 mb-md-0'>
          <div class='copyright'>
